---
export const prerender = true;

import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import GoldInvestmentCalculator from '../../components/tools/GoldInvestmentCalculator';

const title = 'Gold Investment Calculator Pakistan 2026 — Live 24K Gold Prices';
const description =
  'Calculate the current value of your gold holdings in Pakistan using live 24K gold prices (tolas and grams). Includes USD equivalent and price scenario analysis: −20% to +50%.';
const pageUrl = 'https://hisaabkar.pk/tools/gold-price-calculator-pakistan';
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'WebApplication',
    name: title,
    description,
    url: pageUrl,
    applicationCategory: 'FinanceApplication',
    operatingSystem: 'Web, Android, iOS',
    offers: { '@type': 'Offer', price: '0', priceCurrency: 'PKR' },
    featureList: 'Live 24K PMEX gold prices, PKR and USD value, Tola and gram inputs, Scenario analysis -20% to +50%, Portfolio value calculator',
    inLanguage: 'en-PK',
    publisher: { '@type': 'Organization', name: 'HisaabKar.pk', url: 'https://hisaabkar.pk' },
  })} />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
    itemListElement: [
      { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: 'https://hisaabkar.pk' },
      { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Tools', item: 'https://hisaabkar.pk/tools' },
      { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 3, name: 'Gold Price Calculator', item: pageUrl },
    ],
  })} />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'FAQPage',
    mainEntity: [
      {
        '@type': 'Question',
        name: 'What is the gold price per tola in Pakistan today?',
        acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: 'The current 24K gold price per tola in Pakistan is shown live in this calculator, sourced from PMEX (Pakistan Mercantile Exchange). 1 tola = 11.6638 grams. Gold prices update daily based on international spot prices converted at the SBP USD/PKR interbank rate.' },
      },
      {
        '@type': 'Question',
        name: 'How much is 10 tola of gold worth in USD?',
        acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: '10 tolas = 116.638 grams of gold. At international gold price of approximately $3,200/troy ounce (May 2026), 10 tolas ≈ $1,200 USD. In PKR at current rates, 10 tolas ≈ PKR 5.2–5.5 million. The calculator above shows the exact USD equivalent based on live SBP interbank rates.' },
      },
      {
        '@type': 'Question',
        name: 'Is gold a good investment in Pakistan in 2026?',
        acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: 'Gold has historically been an excellent hedge against PKR depreciation and inflation in Pakistan. Over the past decade, gold in PKR has delivered strong returns largely because of currency weakness. However, with National Savings certificates offering 13–15% returns and inflation near 1% in 2026, NSCs now offer better real returns than gold in the near term. Gold works best as 10–20% of a diversified portfolio for long-term PKR protection.' },
      },
      {
        '@type': 'Question',
        name: 'How do I calculate Zakat on my gold?',
        acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: 'Zakat on gold is 2.5% of the market value of gold held above the nisab (87.48g for Gold Nisab, or any amount if total wealth exceeds Silver Nisab). Use the Zakat Calculator on HisaabKar.pk which applies today\'s live gold prices automatically. Example: 200g of 24K gold at PKR 41,975/gram = PKR 8,395,000 value → Zakat = PKR 209,875.' },
      },
      {
        '@type': 'Question',
        name: 'What is the difference between 24K, 22K, and 18K gold price in Pakistan?',
        acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: '24K gold is 99.9% pure (investment/bar gold). 22K is 91.7% pure (standard bridal jewellery in Pakistan) — priced at 22/24 × 24K rate. 18K is 75% pure (modern fine jewellery) — priced at 18/24 × 24K rate. For example, if 24K is PKR 41,975/gram, then 22K ≈ PKR 38,477/gram and 18K ≈ PKR 31,481/gram before jeweller markup.' },
      },
    ],
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">

    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-green-700">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <a href="/tools" class="hover:text-green-700">Tools</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <span>Gold Price Calculator</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">{title}</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6 text-sm">
      Enter your gold quantity to see its current PKR and USD value, plus how different price scenarios
      would affect your portfolio. Data sourced from PMEX via HisaabKar.pk.
    </p>

    <GoldInvestmentCalculator client:load />

    <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg text-xs text-amber-800">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Gold prices are updated periodically and may not reflect real-time
      market rates. This calculator is for informational purposes only and does not constitute
      investment advice. Consult a qualified financial advisor before making investment decisions.
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ / SEO content -->
    <div class="mt-12 prose prose-sm max-w-none text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mt-5 mb-2">What is today's gold rate per tola in Pakistan?</h3>
      <p>Shown live in the calculator above, sourced from PMEX and updated daily. 1 tola = 11.6638 grams. Gold rates change with international spot price and USD/PKR exchange rate.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mt-5 mb-2">How much is 10 tolas of gold in USD?</h3>
      <p>10 tolas = 116.638 grams ≈ $1,200 USD at ~$3,200/troy oz international price (May 2026). The calculator shows exact USD equivalent based on live SBP rates.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mt-5 mb-2">Is gold a good investment in Pakistan 2026?</h3>
      <p>Gold is a proven PKR depreciation hedge. With NSCs offering 13–15% and inflation near 1%, NSCs offer better near-term real returns — but gold provides portfolio diversification and currency protection. 10–20% gold allocation is a common recommendation.</p>

      <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mt-5 mb-2">24K vs 22K vs 18K gold price difference?</h3>
      <p>If 24K = PKR 41,975/g, then 22K ≈ PKR 38,477/g (×0.9167) and 18K ≈ PKR 31,481/g (×0.75). Bridal jewellery is typically 22K. Investment bars are 24K.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
